Upstream-Name: netcode
Upstream-Contact: Glenn Fiedler <glenn@mas-bandwidth.com>
Source: https://github.com/mas-bandwidth/netcode
Comment: The sodium/ directory is a pruned, amalgamated copy of libsodium.
 The Debian package is built with -DNETCODE_SYSTEM_SODIUM=ON, so the
 vendored copy is not compiled into the binary package — the system
 libsodium is used instead. For the official Debian archive the vendored
 copy should additionally be stripped from the orig tarball via
 Files-Excluded (see DEBIAN.md in the packaging repository).

